description:
Julien Laurens and Nedum Onuoha discuss Arsenal's 3-2 victory over Liverpool in the Premier League and ask how far this Arsenal side can go and whether Mo Salah can find his form for the Reds again. The guys also discuss AC Milan's 2-0 win over Juventus, Der Klassiker between Bayern Munich and Borussia Dortmund & pay respects to Franck Ribery amid reports of his impending retirement.
